    "description": {
      "content": "The ReadMe Developer Metrics API powers the Developer Dashboard. It accepts API request logs from Metrics SDKs (Node.js, Python, Ruby, PHP, .NET) and exposes analytics including page quality scores, page view statistics, and search analytics so teams can investigate API usage by key or email and debug requests in real time.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: ReadMe Support",
